snippet.title: Mera First Look - MCU vs DCEU Costumes Review!
snippet.description:
Mera First Look today! Amber Heard in Justice League 2017 reaction! Beyond The Trailer's review & breakdown of MCU vs DCEU Costumes!
http://bit.ly/subscribeBTT

Mera First Look today! Amber Heard in Justice League 2017 vs other female costumes from Marvel and DC movies? Beyond The Trailer host Grace Randolph's reaction and review of the best and worst female costumes in Marvel and DCU aka DC movies today! In this breakdown find out where Harley Quinn, Black Widow, Gamora, Nebula, Wonder Woman, Sif, Scarlet Witch, Enchantress, Katana, Wasp and Mera rank! Share your own reaction and review today even though you haven't yet seen Mera in the full movie Justice League 2017!  And be sure to make Beyond The Trailer your first stop for movie and entertainment news here on YouTube today!
